extracted_metadata.title: Webinar: Christmas in Palestine with Sabeel
extracted_metadata.description: The Green Olive Collective invited Omar Haramy of Sabeel to explore Palestinian Christian perspectives on theology and liberation. Although the video is free to watch, please contribute towards our costs at https://greenolivetours.com/contribut... â€¢ 10% is donated to the Palestine Children's Relief Fund (PCRF). Sabeel,the Ecumenical Liberation Theology Center in Jerusalem, draws on Christian narratives and teachings as a source of resilience in the face of violent military occupation, and develops a Christian spiritual practice that centers the sanctity of the most marginalized.
